paragraph.value: Table 2 shows the main comparison results on the BioCreative CPR testset, with comparisons to the previous state-of-the-art and our baselines.  TEXTONLY gives a performance comparable with Bran. With 1-best dependency trees, our DEPTREE baseline gives better performances than the previous state of the art.  both KBESTEISNERPS and EDGEWISEPS obtain significantly higher numbers than DEPTREE.
